    public interface IDataResponseListener<T>
    This class is the base class of response listeners. Specific response listeners should be derived from this class.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      abstract void onError(Error error)
      Method that will be called when the request was not successful.
      abstract void onResult(T data)
      Method that will be called when the request was successful and the response is good.
